Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Lezo Elementary School in the Municipality of Lezo, Province of Aklan, to the Don Simeon Mobo Reyes Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 821
An Act Changing the Name of the Lezo Elementary School in the Municipality of Lezo, Province of Aklan, to the Don Simeon Mobo Reyes Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Lezo Elementary School in the Municipality of Lezo, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Don Simeon Mobo Reyes Memorial Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
